ET-Partition License Information
=================================

This repository consolidates code from multiple sources, each with its own license.
The licensing for this consolidated repository is MIXED, inheriting from the upstream
projects as detailed below.

本仓库整合了多个来源的代码，每个来源都有自己的许可证。
本整合仓库的许可为混合许可，继承自上游项目，详情如下。

---

COMPONENT LICENSES / 组件许可证
=================================

1. uWUE Method (methods/uwue/)
   Author: Implementation based on Zhou et al. (2016)
   License: Adapted from bigleaf R package and original implementation
   Original Paper: https://doi.org/10.1002/2015WR017766

   Note: bigleaf R package is GPL-3
   Reference: https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=bigleaf

2. TEA Method (methods/tea/)
   Author: Jacob A. Nelson et al.
   License: See methods/tea/LICENSE
   Original Repository: https://github.com/jnelson18/ecosystem-transpiration
   DOI: https://zenodo.org/badge/latestdoi/121650199
   Original Paper: https://doi.org/10.5194/bg-15-2433-2018

3. Perez-Priego Method (methods/perez_priego/)
   Author: Implementation based on Perez-Priego et al. (2018)
   License: Research/Educational Use
   Original Paper: https://doi.org/10.1029/2018JG004637

4. Integration Code and Documentation
   Author: Changming Li (with assistance from Gemini & Claude AI)
   Date: 2025
   License: MIT License (see below)
   Includes: Project structure, batch processing, tests, documentation

